4. Competitions
----------------

The following competitions will be held:
        * AMIGA DEMO    -       Maximum size is 5Mb.
        * AMIGA 40Kb    -       Maximum size is 40960 bytes.
        * AMIGA 4Kb     -       Maximum size is 4096 bytes.
        * FASTINTRO     -       More info at the party itself :)

        * GRAPHICS      -       Please use ONLY one of these formats:
                                IFF/GIF/JPEG.
        * 4 CHANNEL     -       Music will be played with Protracker 3.61.
        * MULTICHANNEL  -       We can play the following formats:
                                Symphonie, Octamed (SS), Digibooster, S3M
                                and XM. Please don't use any other formats ;)

        * WILD COMPO    -       Anything you want ;). Please keep in mind that
                                we only have Amiga computers over there. If you
                                make something on another format, make sure
                                you can attach the computer to the projector!
                                (It uses a standard CINCH CVBS plug).
                                We'll also have a VHS VCR ready, so feel free
                                to hand in any tapes.

The machines used for the competitions will be one of these (you can specify
the computer you want it on at the partyplace):
        - A4000/040 at 25Mhz (2Mb CHIP + 16Mb FAST)
        - A1200/020 at 14Mhz (2Mb CHIP + 0Mb FAST)
        - A1200/030 at 50Mhz (2Mb CHIP + 16Mb FAST) and 50Mhz FPU.

We also have some heavy surprise competitions, but we're not gonna reveal
those in here!!! (Read: It will be LOTS of fun! :)

Prizes will include hard- and software from our loyal sponsors, and
the remainder of the entrance fees.

